From 4a14c14638f7fc76e7826bf13f8f338ed60ff2d1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vincenzo Grimaldi <vince.ceccarelli@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 15:50:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(ui): AWS-pattern header/footer + Ken Burns hero reel

Header (AWS layout pattern, PaintForge content):
- Two-tier: dark utility bar (Contact, Product Preview, Pilot Program)
  above white primary nav with logo, Discover dropdown, links, CTA

Footer (AWS layout pattern, PaintForge content):
- 5 dense columns: Learn / Product / Solutions / Company / Legal
- 'Back to top' divider row; #top anchor on <html> works on every page
- Bottom bar: pre-launch statement + 9 clickable social icons + legal
  line with Privacy/Terms/contact email/copyright

Hero:
- New HeroReel component: 8 Unsplash image slots, preloaded and
  failure-filtered (dead URL can never break the hero), Fisher-Yates
  shuffled on every page load so rotation order differs per visit
- 4 Ken Burns motion variants (zoom-in TL, zoom-out BR, pan right,
  pan up) with 1.8s crossfade, navy legibility overlays, and
  prefers-reduced-motion support

Socials:
- All 9 icons clickable now, pointing at each platform's site until
  PaintForge profiles exist; profile URL formats documented inline
